1266
02:19:35,000 --> 02:19:37,323
- Twelve.
- That's 1,200 euros.

1267
02:19:50,291 --> 02:19:53,954
Professor,
I'm here for my hyperhidrosis.

1268
02:19:54,333 --> 02:19:56,537
