1308
02:25:55,750 --> 02:25:59,199
<i>This piece of furniture
looks great..</i>

1309
02:25:59,500 --> 02:26:03,244
<i>I'd never have thought
of putting it in the bathroom.</i>

1310
02:26:03,416 --> 02:26:06,830
<i>It looks great,
like a new bathroom!</i>

1311
02:26:07,166 --> 02:26:09,537
<i>Well done, Andrea!</i>

1312
